---
/** summate-style founder message — short, personal, honest. */
import CanadianFlag from "../layout/CanadianFlag.astro";
---

<section class="safe-x py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-2xl">
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-8 shadow-soft sm:p-10">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand">From the team</p>
      <blockquote class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-foreground/90">
        <p>
          We're a small Canadian team building the inventory tool we kept wishing existed — real manufacturing depth, honest pricing, and no six-week
          implementation project.
        </p>
        <p>
          Stocklore is in open beta, which means early users genuinely shape what gets built next. Come kick the tires, and tell us what your business needs.
        </p>
      </blockquote>
      <p class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-2 font-heading font-bold">
        — The Stocklore team
        <CanadianFlag class="h-3.5 w-auto" />
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
